		{
			dependencies: ["F012"]
			description: [
				"Drowned lurk in rivers, oceans, and flooded ruins. Those with Tridents will throw them — watch for the wind-up before they release."
				""
				"Underwater combat is slowed without Aqua Affinity and Depth Strider. Fight on the surface edge where possible."
				""
				"§aAqua Dashers§r grant superior underwater movement — essential for ocean monuments, shipwrecks, and any deep-water fight."
